{"type": "article", "id": 21606, "title": "Wearable Habitation coat", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-01T01:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135146o5mh9vplCQDwxAKy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>这件白色的衣服可以用来做睡袋甚至帐篷，设计来自皇家艺术学院（Royal College of Art）的一群学生。他们使用了 Tyvek(特卫强)材料，一种广泛运用于医疗卫生的轻质材料，也有保温的功能。完全摊开后大致是三角形的，可以拉起黑色拉链成为睡袋，经过特殊的折叠后就是一件带帽子的宽松的衣服，适合徒步旅行的年轻人。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/873662572/syrian-refugee-wearable-dwelling\">点击众筹链接可以看到视频信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135143UJi2SKBI4HQr70FG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.03311966\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135144sv5bnduTRjPEZpWM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44764957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135144Fr7Lz4HSuPpXW6cv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.14529915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135145l3V0nJZkeK91yTfL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.95940171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061351458k5C7xXYb3QjoO09.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32051282\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}